quran[109]{c,v,t}:
  10,1,‘ELIF-LAM-RA TILKE ‘AJATUL-KITABIL-HEKIMI
  10,2,‘EKANE LILNNASI ‘AXHEBÆN ‘EN ‘EWHEJNA ‘ILA REXHULIN MINHUM ‘EN ‘ENDHIRI EN-NASE WE BESHSHIRIL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘ENNE LEHUM KADEME SIDKIN ‘INDE RABBIHIM KALEL-KAFIRUNE ‘INNE HADHA LESAHIRUN MUBINUN
  10,3,‘INNE REBBEKUMU ELLAHUL-LEDHI HALEKA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE FI SITTETI ‘EJJAMIN THUMME ESTEWA ‘ALEL-’ARSHI JUDEBBIRUL-’EMRE MA MIN SHEFI’IN ‘ILLA MIN BA’DI ‘IDHNIHI DHELIKUMU ELLAHU REBBUKUM FA’BUDUHU ‘EFELA TEDHEKKERUNE
  10,4,‘ILEJHI MERXHI’UKUM XHEMI’ÆN WA’DEL-LAHI HEKKÆN ‘INNEHU JEBDE’UL-HALKA THUMME JU’IDUHU LIJEXHZIJEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI BIL-KISTI WEL-LEDHINE KEFERU LEHUM SHERABUN MIN HEMIMIN WE ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN BIMA KANU JEKFURUNE
  10,5,HUWEL-LEDHI XHE’ALE ESH-SHEMSE DIJA’EN WEL-KAMERE NURÆN WE KADDEREHU MENAZILE LITA’LEMU ‘ADEDE ES-SININE WEL-HISABE MA HALEKAL-LAHU DHALIKE ‘ILLA BIL-HEKKI JUFESSILUL-’AJATI LIKAWMIN JA’LEMUNE
  10,6,‘INNE FI EHTILAFIL-LEJLI WE EN-NEHARI WE MA HALEKAL-LAHU FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI LE’AJATIN LIKAWMIN JETTEKUNE
  10,7,‘INNEL-LEDHINE LA JERXHUNE LIKA’ENA WE REDU BIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA WE ETME’ENNU BIHA WEL-LEDHINE HUM ‘AN ‘AJATINA GAFILUNE
  10,8,‘ULA’IKE ME’WAHUMU EN-NARU BIMA KANU JEKSIBUNE
  10,9,‘INNEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI JEHDIHIM REBBUHUM BI’IMANIHIM TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHIMUL-’ENHARU FI XHENNATI EN-NA’IMI
  10,10,DA’WAHUM FIHA SUBHANEKEL-LEHUMME WE TEHIJETUHUM FIHA SELAMUN WE ‘AHIRU DA’WAHUM ‘ENIL-HEMDU LILLAHI RABBIL-’ALEMINE
  10,11,WE LEW JU’AXHXHILU ELLAHU LILNNASI ESH-SHERRE ESTI’XHALEHUM BIL-HAJRI LEKUDIJE ‘ILEJHIM ‘EXHELUHUM FENEDHERUL-LEDHINE LA JERXHUNE LIKA’ENA FI TUGJANIHIM JA’MEHUNE
  10,12,WE ‘IDHA MESSEL-’INSANE ED-DURRU DA’ANA LIXHENBIHI ‘EW KA’IDÆN ‘EW KA’IMÆN FELEMMA KESHEFNA ‘ANHU DURREHU MERRE KE’EN LEM JED’UNA ‘ILA DURRIN MESSEHU KEDHALIKE ZUJJINE LILMUSRIFINE MA KANU JA’MELUNE
  10,13,WE LEKAD ‘EHLEKNAL-KURUNE MIN KABLIKUM LEMMA DHELEMU WE XHA’ET/HUM RUSULUHUM BIL-BEJJINATI WE MA KANU LIJU’UMINU KEDHALIKE NEXHZIL-KAWMEL-MUXHRIMINE
  10,14,THUMME XHE’ALNAKUM HALA’IFE FIL-’ERDI MIN BA’DIHIM LINENDHURE KEJFE TA’MELUNE
  10,15,WE ‘IDHA TUTLA ‘ALEJHIM ‘AJATUNA BEJJINATIN KALEL-LEDHINE LA JERXHUNE LIKA’ENA E’TI BIKUR’ANIN GAJRI HADHA ‘EW BEDDILHU KUL MA JEKUNU LI ‘EN ‘UBEDDILEHU MIN TILKA’I NEFSI ‘IN ‘ETTEBI’U ‘ILLA MA JUHA ‘ILEJJE ‘INNI ‘EHAFU ‘IN ‘ASEJTU RABBI ‘ADHABE JEWMIN ‘A
  10,16,KUL LEW SHA’EL-LAHU MA TELEWTUHU ‘ALEJKUM WE LA ‘EDRAKUM BIHI FEKAD LEBITHTU FIKUM ‘UMURÆN MIN KABLIHI ‘EFELA TA’KILUNE
  10,17,FEMEN ‘EDHLEMU MIMMENI EFTERA ‘ALA ELLAHI KEDHIBÆN ‘EW KEDHDHEBE BI’AJATIHI ‘INNEHU LA JUFLIHUL-MUXHRIMUNE
  10,18,WE JA’BUDUNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI MA LA JEDURRUHUM WE LA JENFA’UHUM WE JEKULUNE HA’UULA’ SHUFA’A’UUNA ‘INDEL-LAHI KUL ‘ETUNEBBI’UNEL-LAHE BIMA LA JA’LEMU FI ES-SEMAWATI WE LA FIL-’ERDI SUBHANEHU WE TA’ALA ‘AMMA JUSHRIKUNE
  10,19,WE MA KANE EN-NASU ‘ILLA ‘UMMETEN WAHIDETEN FAHTELEFU WE LEWLA KELIMETUN SEBEKAT MIN RABBIKE LEKUDIJE BEJNEHUM FIMA FIHI JEHTELIFUNE
  10,20,WE JEKULUNE LEWLA ‘UNZILE ‘ALEJHI ‘AJETUN MIN RABBIHI FEKUL ‘INNEMAL-GAJBU LILLAHI FANTEDHIRU ‘INNI ME’AKUM MINEL-MUNTEDHIRINE
  10,21,WE ‘IDHA ‘EDHEKNA EN-NASE REHMETEN MIN BA’DI DERRA’E MESSET/HUM ‘IDHA LEHUM MEKRUN FI ‘AJATINA KULI ELLAHU ‘ESRA’U MEKRÆN ‘INNE RUSULENA JEKTUBUNE MA TEMKURUN
  10,22,HUWEL-LEDHI JUSEJJIRUKUM FIL-BERRI WEL-BEHRI HETTA ‘IDHA KUNTUM FIL-FULKI WE XHEREJNE BIHIM BIRIHIN TEJJIBETIN WE FERIHU BIHA XHA’ET/HA RIHUN ‘ASIFUN WE XHA’EHUMUL-MEWXHU MIN KULLI MEKANIN WE DHENNU ‘ENNEHUM ‘UHITE BIHIM DE’AW ELLAHE MUHLISINE LEHU ED-DIN
  10,23,FELEMMA ‘ENXHAHUM ‘IDHA HUM JEBGUNE FIL-’ERDI BIGAJRIL-HEKKI JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU ‘INNEMA BEGJUKUM ‘ALA ‘ENFUSIKUM META’AL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA THUMME ‘ILEJNA MERXHI’UKUM FENUNEBBI’UKUM BIMA KUNTUM TA’MELUNE
  10,24,‘INNEMA METHELUL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA KEMA’IN ‘ENZELNAHU MINE ES-SEMA’I FAHTELETE BIHI NEBATUL-’ERDI MIMMA JE’KULU EN-NASU WEL-’EN’AM HETTA ‘IDHA ‘EHADHETIL-’ERDU ZUHRUFEHA WE EZZEJJENET WE DHENNE ‘EHLUHA ‘ENNEHUM KADIRUNE ‘ALEJHA ‘ETAHA ‘EMRUNA LEJLÆN ‘EW NEH
  10,25,WEL-LAHU JED’U ‘ILA DARI ES-SELAMI WE JEHDI MEN JESHA’U ‘ILA SIRATIN MUSTEKIMIN
  10,26,LILLEDHINE ‘EHSENUL-HUSNA WE ZIJADETUN WE LA JERHEKU WUXHUHEHUM KATERUN WE LA DHILLETUN ‘ULA’IKE ‘ESHABUL-XHENNETI HUM FIHA HALIDUNE
  10,27,WEL-LEDHINE KESEBU ES-SEJJI’ATI XHEZA’U SEJJI’ETIN BIMITHLIHA WE TERHEKUHUM DHILLETUN MA LEHUM MINEL-LAHI MIN ‘ASIMIN KE’ENNEMA ‘UGSHIJET WUXHUHUHUM KITA’ÆN MINEL-LEJLI MUDHLIMÆN ‘ULA’IKE ‘ESHABU EN-NARI HUM FIHA HALIDUNE
  10,28,WE JEWME NEHSHURUHUM XHEMI’ÆN THUMME NEKULU LILLEDHINE ‘ESHREKU MEKANEKUM ‘ENTUM WE SHUREKA’UUKUM FEZEJJELNA BEJNEHUM WE KALE SHUREKA’UUHUM MA KUNTUM ‘IJANA TA’BUDUNE
  10,29,FEKEFA BILLAHI SHEHIDÆN BEJNENA WE BEJNEKUM ‘IN KUNNA ‘AN ‘IBADETIKUM LEGAFILINE
  10,30,HUNALIKE TEBLU KULLU NEFSIN MA ‘ESLEFET WE RUDDU ‘ILA ELLAHI MEWLAHUMUL-HEKKI WE DELLE ‘ANHUM MA KANU JEFTERUNE
  10,31,KUL MEN JERZUKUKUM MINE ES-SEMA’I WEL-’ERDI ‘EMMEN JEMLIKU ES-SEM’A WEL-’EBSARE WE MEN JUHRIXHUL-HEJJE MINEL-MEJJITI WE JUHRIXHUL-MEJJITE MINEL-HEJJI WE MEN JUDEBBIRUL-’EMRE FESEJEKULUNEL-LAHU FEKUL ‘EFELA TETTEKUNE
  10,32,FEDHELIKUMU ELLAHU REBBUKUMUL-HEKKU FEMADHA BA’DEL-HEKKI ‘ILLA ED-DELALU FE’ENNA TUSREFUNE
  10,33,KEDHALIKE HEKKAT KELIMETU RABBIKE ‘ALEL-LEDHINE FESEKU ‘ENNEHUM LA JU’UMINUNE
  10,34,KUL HEL MIN SHUREKA’IKUM MEN JEBDE’UL-HALKA THUMME JU’IDUHU KULI ELLAHU JEBDE’UL-HALKA THUMME JU’IDUHU FE’ENNA TU’UFEKUNE
  10,35,KUL HEL MIN SHUREKA’IKUM MEN JEHDI ‘ILAL-HEKKI KULI ELLAHU JEHDI LILHEKKI ‘EFEMEN JEHDI ‘ILAL-HEKKI ‘EHEKKU ‘EN JUTTEBE’A ‘EMMEN LA JEHIDDI ‘ILLA ‘EN JUHDA FEMA LEKUM KEJFE TEHKUMUNE
  10,36,WE MA JETTEBI’U ‘EKTHERUHUM ‘ILLA DHENNÆN ‘INNE EDH-DHENNE LA JUGNI MINEL-HEKKI SHEJ’ÆN ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALIMUN BIMA JEF’ALUNE
  10,37,WE MA KANE HADHAL-KUR’ANU ‘EN JUFTERA MIN DUNI ELLAHI WE LEKIN TESDIKAL-LEDHI BEJNE JEDEJHI WE TEFSILEL-KITABI LA REJBE FIHI MIN RABBIL-’ALEMINE
  10,38,‘EM JEKULUNE EFTERAHU KUL FE’TU BISURETIN MITHLIHI WE ED’U MENI ESTETA’TUM MIN DUNI ELLAHI ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKINE
  10,39,BEL KEDHDHEBU BIMA LEM JUHITU BI’ILMIHI WE LEMMA JE’TIHIM TE’WILUHU KEDHALIKE KEDHDHEBEL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM FANDHUR KEJFE KANE ‘AKIBETU EDH-DHALIMINE
  10,40,WE MINHUM MEN JU’UMINU BIHI WE MINHUM MEN LA JU’UMINU BIHI WE REBBUKE ‘A’LEMU BIL-MUFSIDINE
  10,41,WE ‘IN KEDHDHEBUKE FEKUL LI ‘AMELI WE LEKUM ‘AMELUKUM ‘ENTUM BERI’UNE MIMMA ‘A’MELU WE ‘ENA BERI’UN MIMMA TA’MELUNE
  10,42,WE MINHUM MEN JESTEMI’UNE ‘ILEJKE ‘EFE’ENTE TUSMI’U ES-SUMME WE LEW KANU LA JA’KILUNE
  10,43,WE MINHUM MEN JENDHURU ‘ILEJKE ‘EFE’ENTE TEHDIL-’UMJE WE LEW KANU LA JUBSIRUNE
  10,44,‘INNALL-LLAHE LA JEDHLIMU EN-NASE SHEJ’ÆN WE LEKINNE EN-NASE ‘ENFUSEHUM JEDHLIMUNE
  10,45,WE JEWME JEHSHURUHUM KE’EN LEM JELBETHU ‘ILLA SA’ATEN MINE EN-NEHARI JETA’AREFUNE BEJNEHUM KAD HASIREL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU BILIKA’I ELLAHI WE MA KANU MUHTEDINE
  10,46,WE ‘IMMA NURIJENNEKE BA’DEL-LEDHI NA’IDUHUM ‘EW NETEWEFFEJENNEKE FE’ILEJNA MERXHI’UHUM THUMMEL-LAHU SHEHIDUN ‘ALA MA JEF’ALUNE
  10,47,WE LIKULLI ‘UMMETIN RESULUN FE’IDHA XHA’E RESULUHUM KUDIJE BEJNEHUM BIL-KISTI WE HUM LA JUDHLEMUNE
  10,48,WE JEKULUNE META HADHAL-WA’DU ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKINE
  10,49,KUL LA ‘EMLIKU LINEFSI DERRÆN WE LA NEF’ÆN ‘ILLA MA SHA’EL-LAHU LIKULLI ‘UMMETIN ‘EXHELUN ‘IDHA XHA’E ‘EXHELUHUM FELA JESTE’HIRUNE SA’ATEN WE LA JESTEKDIMUNE
  10,50,KUL ‘ERE’EJTUM ‘IN ‘ETAKUM ‘ADHABUHU BEJATÆN ‘EW NEHARÆN MADHA JESTA’XHILU MINHUL-MUXHRIMUNE
  10,51,‘ETHUMME ‘IDHA MA WEKA’A ‘AMENTUM BIHI ‘AL’ANE WE KAD KUNTUM BIHI TESTA’XHILUNE
  10,52,THUMME KILE LILLEDHINE DHELEMU DHUKU ‘ADHABEL-HULDI HEL TUXHZEWNE ‘ILLA BIMA KUNTUM TEKSIBUNE
  10,53,WE JESTENBI’UNEKE ‘EHEKKUN HUWE KUL ‘I WE RABBI ‘INNEHU LEHEKKUN WE MA ‘ENTUM BIMU’XHIZINE
  10,54,WE LEW ‘ENNE LIKULLI NEFSIN DHELEMET MA FIL-’ERDI LAFTEDET BIHI WE ‘ESERRU EN-NEDAMETE LEMMA RE’EWL-’ADHABE WE KUDIJE BEJNEHUM BIL-KISTI WE HUM LA JUDHLEMUNE
  10,55,‘ELA ‘INNE LILLAHI MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI ‘ELA ‘INNE WA’DEL-LAHI HEKKUN WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHEREHUM LA JA’LEMUNE
  10,56,HUWE JUHJI WE JUMITU WE ‘ILEJHI TURXHA’UNE
  10,57,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU KAD XHA’ETKUM MEW’IDHETUN MIN RABBIKUM WE SHIFA’UN LIMA FI ES-SUDURI WE HUDEN WE REHMETUN LILMU’UMININE
  10,58,KUL BIFEDLI ELLAHI WE BIREHMETIHI FEBIDHALIKE FELJEFREHU HUWE HAJRUN MIMMA JEXHMA’UNE
  10,59,KUL ‘ERE’EJTUM MA ‘ENZELEL-LAHU LEKUM MIN RIZKIN FEXHE’ALTUM MINHU HERAMÆN WE HELALÆN KUL ‘ALLLEHU ‘EDHINE LEKUM ‘EM ‘ALA ELLAHI TEFTERUNE
  10,60,WE MA DHENNUL-LEDHINE JEFTERUNE ‘ALA ELLAHIL-KEDHIBE JEWMEL-KIJAMETI ‘INNALL-LLAHE LEDHU FEDLIN ‘ALA EN-NASI WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHEREHUM LA JESHKURUNE
  10,61,WE MA TEKUNU FI SHE’NIN WE MA TETLU MINHU MIN KUR’ANIN WE LA TA’MELUNE MIN ‘AMELIN ‘ILLA KUNNA ‘ALEJKUM SHUHUDÆN ‘IDH TUFIDUNE FIHI WE MA JA’ZUBU ‘AN RABBIKE MIN MITHKALI DHERRETIN FIL-’ERDI WE LA FI ES-SEMA’I WE LA ‘ESGARE MIN DHALIKE WE LA ‘EKBERE ‘ILLA
  10,62,‘ELA ‘INNE ‘EWLIJA’EL-LAHI LA HAWFUN ‘ALEJHIM WE LA HUM JEHZENUNE
  10,63,EL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE KANU JETTEKUNE
  10,64,LEHUMUL-BUSHRA FIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA WE FIL-’AHIRETI LA TEBDILE LIKELIMATI ELLAHI DHALIKE HUWEL-FEWZUL-’ADHIMU
  10,65,WE LA JEHZUNKE KAWLUHUM ‘INNEL-’IZZETE LILLAHI XHEMI’ÆN HUWE ES-SEMI’UL-’ALIMU
  10,66,‘ELA ‘INNE LILLAHI MEN FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MEN FIL-’ERDI WE MA JETTEBI’UL-LEDHINE JED’UNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI SHUREKA’E ‘IN JETTEBI’UNE ‘ILLA EDH-DHENNE WE ‘IN HUM ‘ILLA JEHRUSUNE
  10,67,HUWEL-LEDHI XHE’ALE LEKUMUL-LEJLE LITESKUNU FIHI WE EN-NEHARE MUBSIRÆN ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJATIN LIKAWMIN JESMA’UNE
  10,68,KALU ETTEHADHEL-LAHU WELEDÆN SUBHANEHU HUWEL-GANIJU LEHU MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MA FIL-’ERDI ‘IN ‘INDEKUM MIN SULTANIN BIHEDHA ‘ETEKULUNE ‘ALA ELLAHI MA LA TA’LEMUNE
  10,69,KUL ‘INNEL-LEDHINE JEFTERUNE ‘ALA ELLAHIL-KEDHIBE LA JUFLIHUNE
  10,70,META’UN FI ED-DUNJA THUMME ‘ILEJNA MERXHI’UHUM THUMME NUDHIKUHUMUL-’ADHABE ESH-SHEDIDE BIMA KANU JEKFURUNE
  10,71,WE ETLU ‘ALEJHIM NEBE’E NUHIN ‘IDH KALE LIKAWMIHI JA KAWMI ‘IN KANE KEBURE ‘ALEJKUM MEKAMI WE TEDHKIRI BI’AJA TI ELLAHI FE’ALA ELLAHI TEWEKKELTU FE’EXHMI’U ‘EMREKUM WE SHUREKA’EKUM THUMME LA JEKUN ‘EMRUKUM ‘ALEJKUM GUMMETEN THUMME EKDU ‘ILEJJE WE LA TUNDH
  10,72,FE’IN TEWELLEJTUM FEMA SE’ELTUKUM MIN ‘EXHRIN ‘IN ‘EXHRI ‘ILLA ‘ALA ELLAHI WE ‘UMIRTU ‘EN ‘EKUNE MINEL-MUSLIMINE
  10,73,FEKEDHDHEBUHU FENEXHXHEJNAHU WE MEN ME’AHU FIL-FULKI WE XHE’ALNAHUM HALA’IFE WE ‘EGREKNAL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATINA FANDHUR KEJFE KANE ‘AKIBETUL-MUNDHERINE
  10,74,THUMME BE’ATHNA MIN BA’DIHI RUSULÆN ‘ILA KAWMIHIM FEXHA’UHUM BIL-BEJJINATI FEMA KANU LIJU’UMINU BIMA KEDHDHEBU BIHI MIN KABLU KEDHALIKE NETBA’U ‘ALA KULUBIL-MU’TEDINE
  10,75,THUMME BE’ATHNA MIN BA’DIHIM MUSA WE HARUNE ‘ILA FIR’AWNE WE MELE’IHI BI’AJATINA FASTEKBERU WE KANU KAWMÆN MUXHRIMINE
  10,76,FELEMMA XHA’EHUMUL-HEKKU MIN ‘INDINA KALU ‘INNE HADHA LESIHRUN MUBINUN
  10,77,KALE MUSA ‘ETEKULUNE LILHEKKI LEMMA XHA’EKUM ‘ESIHRUN HADHA WE LA JUFLIHU ES-SAHIRUNE
  10,78,KALU ‘EXHI’TENA LITELFITENA ‘AMMA WEXHEDNA ‘ALEJHI ‘ABA’ENA WE TEKUNE LEKUMAL-KIBRIJA’U FIL-’ERDI WE MA NEHNU LEKUMA BIMU’UMININE
  10,79,WE KALE FIR’AWNU E’TUNI BIKULLI SAHIRIN ‘ALIMIN
  10,80,FELEMMA XHA’E ES-SEHERETU KALE LEHUM MUSA ‘ELKU MA ‘ENTUM MULKUNE
  10,81,FELEMMA ‘ELKAW KALE MUSA MA XHI’TUM BIHI ES-SIHRU ‘INNALL-LLAHE SEJUBTILUHU ‘INNALL-LLAHE LA JUSLIHU ‘AMELEL-MUFSIDINE
  10,82,WE JUHIKKU ELLAHUL-HEKKA BIKELIMATIHI WE LEW KERIHEL-MUXHRIMUNE
  10,83,FEMA ‘AMENE LIMUSA ‘ILLA DHURRIJETUN MIN KAWMIHI ‘ALA HAWFIN MIN FIR’AWNE WE MELE’IHIM ‘EN JEFTINEHUM WE ‘INNE FIR’AWNE LA’ALIN FIL-’ERDI WE ‘INNEHU LEMINEL-MUSRIFINE
  10,84,WE KALE MUSA JA KAWMI ‘IN KUNTUM ‘AMENTUM BILLAHI FE’ALEJHI TEWEKKELU ‘IN KUNTUM MUSLIMINE
  10,85,FEKALU ‘ALA ELLAHI TEWEKKELNA REBBENA LA TEXH’ALNA FITNETEN LILKAWMI EDH-DHALIMINE
  10,86,WE NEXHXHINA BIREHMETIKE MINEL-KAWMIL-KAFIRINE
  10,87,WE ‘EWHEJNA ‘ILA MUSA WE ‘EHIHI ‘EN TEBEWWE’A LIKAWMIKUMA BIMISRE BUJUTÆN WE EXH’ALU BUJUTEKUM KIBLETEN WE ‘EKIMU ES-SELÆTE WE BESHSHIRIL-MU’UMININE
  10,88,WE KALE MUSA REBBENA ‘INNEKE ‘ATEJTE FIR’AWNE WE MELE’EHU ZINETEN WE ‘EMWALÆN FIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA REBBENA LIJUDILLU ‘AN SEBILIKE REBBENA ETMIS ‘ALA ‘EMWALIHIM WE ESHDUD ‘ALA KULUBIHIM FELA JU’UMINU HETTA JEREWL-’ADHABEL-’ELIME
  10,89,KALE KAD ‘UXHIBET DA’WETUKUMA FASTEKIMA WE LA TETTEBI’ANI SEBILEL-LEDHINE LA JA’LEMUNE
  10,90,WE XHAWEZNA BIBENI ‘ISRA’ILEL-BEHRE FE’ETBE’AHUM FIR’AWNU WE XHUNUDUHU BEGJÆN WE’ADWEN HETTA ‘IDHA ‘EDREKEHUL-GAREKU KALE ‘AMENTU ‘ENNEHU LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLAL-LEDHI ‘AMENET BIHI BENU ‘ISRA’ILE WE ‘ENA MINEL-MUSLIMINE
  10,91,‘AL’ANE WE KAD ‘ASEJTE KABLU WE KUNTE MINEL-MUFSIDINE
  10,92,FALJEWME NUNEXHXHIKE BIBEDENIKE LITEKUNE LIMEN HALFEKE ‘AJETEN WE ‘INNE KETHIRÆN MINE EN-NASI ‘AN ‘AJATINA LEGAFILUNE
  10,93,WE LEKAD BEWWE’NA BENI ‘ISRA’ILE MUBEWWE’E SIDKIN WE REZEKNAHUM MINET-TEJJIBATI FEMA EHTELEFU HETTA XHA’EHUMUL-’ILMU ‘INNE REBBEKE JEKDI BEJNEHUM JEWMEL-KIJAMETI FIMA KANU FIHI JEHTELIFUNE
  10,94,FE’IN KUNTE FI SHEKKIN MIMMA ‘ENZELNA ‘ILEJKE FAS’ELIL-LEDHINE JEKRE’UNEL-KITABE MIN KABLIKE LEKAD XHA’EKEL-HEKKU MIN RABBIKE FELA TEKUNENNE MINEL-MUMTERINE
  10,95,WE LA TEKUNENNE MINEL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATI ELLAHI FETEKUNE MINEL-HASIRINE
  10,96,‘INNEL-LEDHINE HEKKAT ‘ALEJHIM KELIMETU RABBIKE LA JU’UMINUNE
  10,97,WE LEW XHA’ET/HUM KULLU ‘AJETIN HETTA JEREWL-’ADHABEL-’ELIME
  10,98,FELEWLA KANET KARJETUN ‘AMENET FENEFE’AHA ‘IMANUHA ‘ILLA KAWME JUNIS LEMMA ‘AMENU KESHEFNA ‘ANHUM ‘ADHABEL-HIZJI FIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA WE METTA’NAHUM ‘ILA HININ
  10,99,WE LEW SHA’E REBBUKE LE’AMENE MEN FIL-’ERDI KULLUHUM XHEMI’ÆN ‘EFE’ENTE TUKRIHU EN-NASE HETTA JEKUNU MU’UMININE
  10,100,WE MA KANE LINEFSIN ‘EN TU’UMINE ‘ILLA BI’IDHNI ELLAHI WE JEXH’ALU ER-RIXHSE ‘ALEL-LEDHINE LA JA’KILUNE
  10,101,KUL ENDHURU MADHA FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE MA TUGNIL-’AJATU WE EN-NUDHURU ‘AN KAWMIN LA JU’UMINUNE
  10,102,FEHEL JENTEDHIRUNE ‘ILLA MITHLE ‘EJJAMIL-LEDHINE HALEW MIN KABLIHIM KUL FANTEDHIRU ‘INNI ME’AKUM MINEL-MUNTEDHIRINE
  10,103,THUMME NUNEXHXHI RUSULENA WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU KEDHALIKE HEKKÆN ‘ALEJNA NUNXHIL-MU’UMININE
  10,104,KUL JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU ‘IN KUNTUM FI SHEKKIN MIN DINI FELA ‘A’BUDUL-LEDHINE TA’BUDUNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI WE LEKIN ‘A’BUDU ELLAHEL-LEDHI JETEWEFFAKUM WE ‘UMIRTU ‘EN ‘EKUNE MINEL-MU’UMININE
  10,105,WE ‘EN ‘EKIM WEXHHEKE LILDDINI HENIFÆN WE LA TEKUNENNE MINEL-MUSHRIKINE
  10,106,WE LA TED’U MIN DUNI ELLAHI MA LA JENFA’UKE WE LA JEDURRUKE FE’IN FE’ALTE FE’INNEKE ‘IDHÆN MINE EDH-DHALIMINE
  10,107,WE ‘IN JEMSESKEL-LAHU BIDURRIN FELA KASHIFE LEHU ‘ILLA HUWE WE ‘IN JURIDKE BIHAJRIN FELA RADDE LIFEDLIHI JUSIBU BIHI MEN JESHA’U MIN ‘IBADIHI WE HUWEL-GAFURU ER-REHIMU
  10,108,KUL JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU KAD XHA’EKUMUL-HEKKU MIN RABBIKUM FEMENI EHTEDA FE’INNEMA JEHTEDI LINEFSIHI WE MEN DELLE FE’INNEMA JEDILLU ‘ALEJHA WE MA ‘ENA ‘ALEJKUM BIWEKILIN
  10,109,WE ETTEBI’ MA JUHA ‘ILEJKE WE ESBIR HETTA JEHKUMEL-LAHU WE HUWE HAJRUL-HAKIMINE